                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 rounded-full text-sm">Node.js</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 rounded-full text-sm">MongoDB</span>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline font-medium">
                  View Project →
